        "reponse": "Il s\u0027agit d\u0027un manquement \u00E0 la probit\u00E9 et \u00E0 l\u0027honn\u00EAtet\u00E9, plus pr\u00E9cis\u00E9ment d\u0027un acte de corruption (d\u00E9tournement de fonds publics).",
